-- Syria Shot Down Turkish Plane, Apologized for It, Haberturk Says
-- B y   B e n j a m i n   H a r v e y
-- 2012-06-22T15:24:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-22/syria-shot-down-turkish-plane-apologized-for-it-haberturk-says.html
Syria has apologized to Turkey for
shooting down a military plane over the Mediterranean, Haberturk
television reported.  The Turkish pilots are alive and Syria has apologized,
saying the shooting was a mistake, Haberturk cited Prime
Minister  Recep Tayyip Erdogan  as saying. He was speaking to
reporters on a plane taking him back from the G20 summit.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Benjamin Harvey in Istanbul at 
